0]静佑0224[/uid] (2026-06-04 13:52):[/b]<br/><br/>看了宝宝王国现在的走势和昨天的回复,就感觉这个无形的大(爪)手(子)也太强了[/quote]<br/>我仁至义尽了  我觉得", "lou": 2941, "content_length": 23, "reply_to": 870591257, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780552499}, {"pid": 870591911, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 449, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 13:57", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "这周末把 我更新一次如果有机会3-5加速最后一次我的策略基础版<br/>希望到时候我心情好 可能写多点。", "lou": 2942, "content_length": 87, "14": {"13": 5, "14": 1}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780552678}, {"pid": 870592502, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 62, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 14:02", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870592337,45974302,6489]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=62867840]白里小生[/uid] (2026-06-04 14:01):[/b]<br/><br/>套定律，混合键设备，抛光液，电镀设备，以及 探针。还有硅片当然少不了[s:ac:瞎][s:ac:瞎] 都是熟悉的朋友。浪大[/quote]<br/>先进封装你为什么不说  你是不是哪里有点什么问题", "lou": 2943, "content_length": 49, "reply_to": 870592337, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780552973}, {"pid": 870594884, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 126, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 14:22", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "就是这根K线了 <br/>压死所有非科技的最后一根稻草。", "lou": 2944, "content_length": 43, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780554179}, {"pid": 870595362, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 75, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 14:26", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870595153,45974302,6494]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67135665]woodk1d[/uid] (2026-06-04 14:25):[/b]<br/><br/>这样的大盘，这样的市场让我真的觉得恶心<br/><br/>这是多少天尾盘开砸、收盘全天最低了？<br/><br/>敢盘中买就被套呗<br/><br/>主力是爽了，每天都有T可做，真的一点不把散户当人，一点不想一起吃蛋糕啊[/quote]<br/>散户本来就不是人 是血包", "lou": 2945, "content_length": 27, "reply_to": 870595153, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780554386}, {"pid": 870596106, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 192, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 14:32", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "接下来到明天中午 你们会看到超绝望割肉盘口", "lou": 2946, "content_length": 40, "14": {"14": 1, "13": 2}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780554733}, {"pid": 870596352, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 52, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 14:34", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870596152,45974302,6497]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38140916]huohuo277[/uid] (2026-06-04 14:32):[/b]<br/><br/>科技也跟着回落啊[/quote]<br/>你看错了 你不信问问他们回落了嘛", "lou": 2947, "content_length": 35, "reply_to": 870596152, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780554848}, {"pid": 870597515, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 146, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 14:42", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我和你们说过的  你们可能忘记了<br/>就像把大象关进冰箱要三步  打开冰箱门  把大象塞进去  关上冰箱门 一样<br/>逼老登里面的活跃资金也是一样<br/>大家一起跌<br/>科技先止跌 他还在跌<br/>他比科技反弹得少<br/>[color=red]科技比他跌得少[/color]---现在就是这个阶段了  因为老登们想着抱团瓦解后钱会到他们那边，一旦发现指数破位抱团都没瓦解的可能性 这就是极限了<br/>普反科技比他反得多<br/>只有科技在涨。<br/><br/>你们多看一下我之前说的小剧场吧", "lou": 2948, "content_length": 341, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780555365}, {"pid": 870598106, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 174, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 14:47", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们看一下量能就懂了<br/>全体机构柚子静默  等老登割肉。<br/>你们出去不要说是我说的啊", "lou": 2949, "content_length": 72, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780555627}, {"pid": 870598953, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 84, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 14:53", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们其实可以看一下  尾盘没有放量的  是继续缩量的<br/>但是科技被很多散单子 一张一张的买起来了  也没人砸  就是一点点的散单子买起来了。", "lou": 2950, "content_length": 118, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780556013}, {"pid": 870599668, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 100, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 14:58", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870599303,45974302,6504]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42380939]暮暮朝朝6[/uid] (2026-06-04 14:56):[/b]<br/><br/>明天要普跌的话 今天要不要把没涨的科技出一部分 等明天捡带血筹码[/quote]<br/>我已经看不出还有普跌的迹象了", "lou": 2951, "content_length": 33, "reply_to": 870599303, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780556337}, {"pid": 870600436, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 79, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 15:04", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870600240,45974302,6506]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67211927]alleriawr9二号机[/uid] (2026-06-04 15:03):[/b]<br/><br/>事到如今已经没人知道第一个说出4317的是谁了，传着传着就传歪了，狼大说的一直是4315[/quote]<br/>其实我真的说的是4317-4375 我没有说过别的数字<br/>我只是不希望你们只看数字 而不知道为什么<br/>我就想问了 你们到底知道这些数字怎么来的么", "lou": 2952, "content_length": 126, "reply_to": 870600240, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780556691}, {"pid": 870601042, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 86, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 15:09", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "今天下午开始的会有很多这段时间从来没买过科技的  买不多  买个几手<br/>这就是撬动资金的含义了", "lou": 2953, "content_length": 82, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780556957}, {"pid": 870601669, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 45, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 15:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870601537,45974302,6507]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67156308]xenoblade4[/uid] (2026-06-04 15:12):[/b]<br/><br/>张小泉能化身光纤设备，我茅台新增个半导体清洗材料概念不过分吧？[/quote]<br/>不行 除非液冷管装茅台  不然行不了一点", "lou": 2954, "content_length": 39, "reply_to": 870601537, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780557226}, {"pid": 870602302, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 62, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 15:18", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870601928,45974302,6508]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42432642]zjsxybkgjd[/uid] (2026-06-04 15:15):[/b]<br/><br/>铁盒能看了么狼大？两根止跌选方向的揉搓线，今天选方向也是红的。[/quote]<br/>我最后一波做个股 我不做ETF", "lou": 2955, "content_length": 30, "reply_to": 870601928, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780557506}, {"pid": 870603033, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 81, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 15:24", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870602684,45974302,6509]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38808210]纯生啤酒[/uid] (2026-06-04 15:21):[/b]<br/><br/>尝到甜头之后就会，开始逐渐挪仓位过来，最后一把爆掉吗[s:ac:怕][/quote]<br/>人最怕的就是比较心理<br/>如果你只持有那些深套的 也就没有这种心思<br/>一旦你的票仓里面 有个只有10手的科技股 可能很快的覆盖你100手的老登股的亏损的时候<br/>你说你心思会不会泛滥一下？", "lou": 2956, "content_length": 166, "reply_to": 870602684, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780557849}, {"pid": 870603954, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 58, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 15:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870603647,45974302,6510]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=1003090]zzh90pk[/uid] (2026-06-04 15:28):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，请教这波整完，半导体是不是可以认为企稳了？还是这整个动作都是反弹过程，预期还会探新低？<br/>我自己不需要，但家里老登真的和你说的哀嚎一模一样，看看能不能起码救进etf里[s:ac:衰][/quote]<br/>趁机夺位 让他们看看以后家里谁话事", "lou": 2957, "content_length": 37, "reply_to": 870603647, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780558250}, {"pid": 870604785, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 39, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-04 15:36", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=870604354,45974302,6511]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61102614]米璐璐6666LLL[/uid] (2026-06-04 15:33):[/b]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202606/04/jmQ6-hapfK22T1k